kettles spring to mind! Just call an election! Get it done!\" A few were pleased. Padpad added: \"Patricia Hewitt and Geoff Hoon calling for secret ballot on Gordon Brown's leadership! Took them long enough. Should've done this a year ago.\" Canny_lass said: \"I'd like to thank Geoff Hoon and Patricia Hewitt for providing the BBC with a news story that doesn't involve snow;).\" And afroirish made an early leadership bid: \"Geoff Hoon and Patricia Hewitt call for secret ballot over Gordon Brown's leadership ... Do you think I could throw my hat into the ring?\"",
